===Noun===
{{en-noun|-}}

# {{chemistry}} A [[nonmetallic]] [[element]] (''symbol'' Si) with an [[atomic number]] of 14 and [[atomic weight]] of 28.0855.

====Usage notes====
# Do not confuse '''silicon''' with '''[[silicone]]'''.

